frames.caption: A young man and a pug sit closely by a window, gazing at each other with a snowy landscape in the background. The scene captures a quiet moment of connection between the two, framed by the softly falling snow outside.

frames.caption: A young person and a small dog sit side by side, gazing out of a large window at a snowy landscape. The person is wearing a cozy, fur-lined coat, while the dog sits attentively, both seemingly captivated by the falling snow.
